{
  "page": "The Dragon and the Wolf",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_7\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 7\">Season 7</a> of the television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i> is partially based on material from the unreleased sixth novel <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> and potentially the unreleased seventh novel <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dream_of_Spring\" title=\"A Dream of Spring\">A Dream of Spring</a></i>. Therefore, this page might contain spoilers for these books.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(248, 233, 208);border:none;\">\"The Dragon and the Wolf\"</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size: 100%\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:right;\">Season 7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">&#160;—&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:left;\">Episode 7</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original air date</th><td>\nAugust 27, 2017</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Running time</th><td>\n80 minutes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Credits</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Directed by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Benioff\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:David Benioff\">David Benioff</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D._B._Weiss\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:D. B. Weiss\">D.B. Weiss</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Episode chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">←&#160;Previous</th>\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">Next&#160;→</th>\n</tr><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall_(TV)\" title=\"Beyond the Wall (TV)\">Beyond the Wall</a>\"</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell_(TV)\" title=\"Winterfell (TV)\">Winterfell</a>\"</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_Game_of_Thrones_episodes\" title=\"List of Game of Thrones episodes\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>\"<b>The Dragon and the Wolf</b>\" is the seventh and final episode of the <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_7\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 7\">seventh season</a> of HBO's fantasy television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, and the 67th overall. The episode was written by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Benioff\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:David Benioff\">David Benioff</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D._B._Weiss\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:D. B. Weiss\">D.B. Weiss</a> and directed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a>. It first aired on August 27, 2017, and had 12.07 million viewers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Official_synopsis\">Official synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Dragon_and_the_Wolf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Official synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tyrion tries to save Westeros from itself. Sansa questions loyalties.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Dragon_and_the_Wolf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Sunday cable ratings: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/more-tv-news/game-of-thrones-season-7-finale-smashes-more-records-for-hbo/\">'Game of Thrones' Season 7 finale smashes more records for HBO</a> TV by the Numbers</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span cla